            "votes_up": 4,
            "weighted_score": 0.5629138946533203,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "1. No option to spawn with belt equiped+engine started+gear \"D\" selected+lights enabled+brake disabled. I am here to perform a lessons, not to putting on seatbelt and turning on the lights over and over again. Very bad UX design.\n\n2. No useful popup tip, when player tries to change gear without brake pedal pressed.\n\n3. No ghost-car that drives ahead of you and show you how to correctly perform a lesson.\n\n4. There is no training of the correct grip of the steering wheel, nor the use of the legs, nor the use of the hands when intercepting the steering wheel to make a turn."
        },
